race.comment: NEED YOU NOW (3) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind MIGHTY HERCULES (26.43) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to give a sight. Leading chance again. MIGHTY HERCULES (7) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by one length at this track in a handy 26.35 beating Black In Style. Ran the fastest time on the program in his latest win. Likely to be in the finish. AMRON TOMMY (2) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (29.69) in a Grade 5 at Sale. Solid record at the distance winning two races. Can figure in the finish. WARRIOR ETHAN (1) can fill a top-three spot.
